1
00:00:00,200 --> 00:00:03,320
Tell me she's lying! Tell me it's not true!

2
00:00:04,120 --> 00:00:06,720
Look at me! In my eyes! Answer me!

3
00:00:07,320 --> 00:00:08,720
Tell me it's not true, come on!

4
00:00:10,160 --> 00:00:11,480
How did Eylül die?

5
00:00:11,760 --> 00:00:13,800
Why are you digging up old issues?

6
00:00:14,400 --> 00:00:16,120
Am I carrying her kidney?

7
00:00:17,080 --> 00:00:19,200
Am I alive because of Eylül!

8
00:00:20,080 --> 00:00:21,880
I saved my precious daughter.

9
00:00:22,640 --> 00:00:24,320
I wish you hadn't!

10
00:00:25,400 --> 00:00:28,480
I wish you had just let me die! Let me die.

11
00:00:29,240 --> 00:00:31,840
Any father who loves his child
would have done what I did.

12
00:00:31,920 --> 00:00:34,160
Do you think I can live like this!

13
00:00:34,240 --> 00:00:37,439
You killed a child, dad!

14
00:00:37,440 --> 00:00:39,760
You sacrificed Eylül for
me! How could you do this!

15
00:00:40,680 --> 00:00:43,080
Why did you tell Mercan
everything even though I warned you?

16
00:00:43,960 --> 00:00:45,000
What do you want from her?

17
00:00:45,760 --> 00:00:46,920
What's your problem?

18
00:00:47,720 --> 00:00:50,920
I'm just trying to protect
my family, protect you.

19
00:00:51,440 --> 00:00:53,200
You're not protecting anyone.

20
00:00:53,640 --> 00:00:57,600
You are hurting my wife, the woman I love.

21
00:00:58,120 --> 00:01:01,160
That sneaky girl destroys
everything she touches.

22
00:01:01,880 --> 00:01:03,880
Look, we're fighting because of her.

23
00:01:03,920 --> 00:01:04,920
Don't!

24
00:01:05,600 --> 00:01:07,960
If you ever do anything
to hurt Mercan again...

25
00:01:08,400 --> 00:01:12,480
or do anything to upset her, know
that there will be no forgiveness.

26
00:01:13,720 --> 00:01:14,720
I will erase you.

27
00:01:15,600 --> 00:01:17,240
Everything started because of me.

28
00:01:18,120 --> 00:01:19,600
The pain that was suffered,

29
00:01:20,600 --> 00:01:21,600
your vow of revenge...

30
00:01:22,800 --> 00:01:24,400
If I had died instead of Eylül...

31
00:01:24,920 --> 00:01:26,760
- none of this would have happened...
- Enough.

32
00:01:27,520 --> 00:01:29,040
There is no consolation for this pain.

33
00:01:30,400 --> 00:01:31,800
You are the only thing I have left.

34
00:01:33,800 --> 00:01:35,280
And I don't want to lose you too.

35
