For subtitles.

525
00:44:05,121 --> 00:44:09,359
Tap settings, choose subtitles,
and pick your language on mobile.

526
00:44:09,360 --> 00:44:12,360
Tap the top CC button
and select your language.

527
00:44:12,520 --> 00:44:14,399
For audio, tap settings.

528
